                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9025" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0288</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1197 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石家庄高新区供水排水公司：独一无二的全民所有制企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Shijiazhuang High-tech Zone Water Supply and Drainage Company: a unique enterprise owned by the whole people</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许长勇，乔彤，刘杰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石家庄高新技术产业开发区供水排水公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">党群部门/思想政治工作部门/企业文化部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">参与式管理；心理所有权；企业文化；公司治理；创新创业管理；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Participative Management;Psychological Ownership;Corporate Culture; Corporate Governance;Innovation and Entrepreneurship Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石家庄高新区供水排水公司是一家成立于1994年4月27日的全民所有制企业，但成立30年来管委会没有拨付任何资金，完全靠个人和集体筹资创办和发展。在成立时政府只给了一个“性质全民、资金自筹、独立核算、自主经营、自负盈亏、民主选举、民主管理、独立承担民事责任”的政策。本案例通过描述公司自成立以来始终实行民主选举，将领导的任命权交给员工；实行工资公开、信息透明，使员工能及时了解企业最新讯息；实行利益共享，员工工资跟随企业收益逐年增加，创建企业内部管乐团，丰富员工精神生活的同时增强团队凝聚力，促进员工主人翁意识的形成，使员工认为自己就是企业的主人；在企业遇到困难时，员工踊跃集资帮助企业度过难关，企业依靠员工做到在全国供水行业普遍亏损的情况下连年实现盈利，甚至自2004年以来，年年为员工涨工资的事例。旨在让学生认识到员工充分参与企业的管理能促使员工对企业产生心理所有权，增强主人翁责任感，进而促进企业的持续健康发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shijiazhuang High-tech Zone Water Supply and Drainage Company is an enterprise owned by the whole people established on April 27,1994. However, since its establishment 30 years ago, the management committee has not allocated any funds and relies on individual and collective financing to establish and develop. At the time of its establishment, the government only gave a policy of providing the whole people, self-raised funds, independent accounting, independent operation, self-responsibility for profits and losses, democratic election, democratic management, and independent civil liability. This case through the description of the company since its inception has always been the implementation of democratic election, giving the appointment of the leaders to the employees; implement salary disclosure and information transparency, so that the employees can timely understand the latest information of the enterprise; implement benefit sharing, employee wages follow the enterprise income to increase year by year, create an internal wind orchestra, enrich the spiritual life of employees and enhance the cohesion of the team, and promote the formation of the sense of ownership of employees, so that employees think that they are the masters of the enterprise. When the enterprise encounters difficulties, the employees actively raise funds to help the enterprise overcome difficulties. The enterprise relies on the employees to achieve profits year after year under the general loss of the national water supply industry. Since 2004, the employees&#39; wages have been raised every year. The purpose is to make students realize that the full participation of employees in enterprise management can promote them to have psychological ownership of the enterprise, enhance the sense of responsibility as masters, and then promote the sustainable and healthy development of the enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业文化》、《公司治理》、《创新创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">心理所有权；参与式管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
